Mike Ansert

EACA’s Sponsorship Chair

Position and details

Mike Ansert is currently EACA’s Sponsorship Chair. Mike graduated from Floyd Central High School in 1991. Attended Indiana University Bloomington, graduating with Finance and Management degree. Mike is married to Dawn Ansert and they have 4 kids. Megan, Graduate of Eastern in 2019, Lauren, currently a Senior at Eastern High School, and Ryan and Will Ansert, who are sophomores at Eastern High School. Mike works in the logistics and supply chain industry spending 25 years with C.H. Robinson but now V.P. or Business Development at BlueGrace Logistics.
